- internal/retro/generator.go - NEW. `Generator` interface; `GenerateRequest` {Subjects []SubjectArtifact (each: covered run id + resolved stage output/inputs as fully-materialized RunInput-style bytes + ArtifactSource provenance), Scope, Trigger, Producer}; `GenerateResult` {Body []byte, MediaType string, Producer runmanifest.Producer}; `StubGenerator` (Canned/Err, echoes req.Producer) with compile-time `var _ Generator` assertion. Mirrors internal/replay/runner.go.
